summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 61E, Page 150 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone certain property in Block 2 of Scenic Park Addition to The City of Seattle, at 41st Avenue Southwest and Southwest Edmonds Street from Multiple Residence/Low Density, (RM 800) to Community Business (BC) Zone. (Petition of Robert F. Hintz; C.F. No. 293031.)
